[TITLE]The Manual: Text Viewers[/TITLE]
Use
[IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_UP]
[IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_DOWN]
[IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_LEFT]
[IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_RIGHT]
[IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_PAGEUP]
[IKEY:STANDARDSCROLL_PAGEDOWN] to scroll.  You can check the key bindings for your current settings.  You can get to the key bindings
by pressing [IKEY:OPTIONS].
[B]Press [IKEY:SECONDSCROLL_DOWN][IKEY:SECONDSCROLL_UP] to move between any highlighted links,
and press [IKEY:SELECT] to select a highlighted link.
Here are some practice links to try:
